,1,'2014-08-24 20:18:02','2014-08-25 03:18:02','<div><img src=\'https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3835/14840508740_bb4ff9f407.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div><br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oBpudm</div></div>','Modern Concert','','publish','closed','open','','modern-concert','','','2014-08-24 20:18:02','2014-08-25 03:18:02','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1397',0,'post','',0),(1399,1,'2014-08-28 20:33:01','2014-08-29 03:33:01','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5567/14882571577_0eb22a9ea7_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Maui is known as the Valley island, I suppose because of what you see here.  Nestled between two volcanic regions, the middle of the island looks lush and beautiful primarily because of irrigation brought in to enable sugar plantations.  Taken from a helicopter tour of the island.\n<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oF852F</div></div>','The Valley','','publish','closed','open','','the-valley','','','2014-08-28 20:33:01','2014-08-29 03:33:01','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1399',0,'post','',0),(1401,1,'2014-08-29 18:23:56','2014-08-30 01:23:56','<div><img src=\'https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3851/15054956356_17b7887cbd_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>SOOC is a photographer acronym for Straight Out Of Camera.  The new Fuji cameras have some great film simulation modes emulating Fuji\'s old films.  In this case, this is a monochrome image with a Red filter to darken the sky.  From Lahaina in Maui. <br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oWmA23</div></div>','SOOC','','publish','closed','open','','sooc','','','2014-08-29 18:23:56','2014-08-30 01:23:56','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1401',0,'post','',0),(1403,1,'2014-09-03 10:21:09','2014-09-03 17:21:09','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5586/14943145987_78fc38694e_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Maui isn\'t all about the beautiful white sand beaches, there\'s some really cool volcanic black sand beaches around the eastern side of the island.  Hard to see, but in the background, there\'s a beautiful small waterfall right on the coast as well.\n<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oLtwG4</div></div>','Black Sand','','publish','closed','open','','black-sand','','','2014-09-03 10:21:09','2014-09-03 17:21:09','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1403',0,'post','',0),(1405,1,'2014-09-11 15:25:52','2014-09-11 22:25:52','<div><img src=\'https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3859/15188209926_cff98e17c3_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>I\'m in Barcelona this week for work but got the afternoon off to explore a bit.  If you get a chance, highly recommend  spending some time in the Gothic Quarter.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/p98xEo</div></div>','Catedral de Barcelona','','publish','closed','open','','catedral-de-barcelona','','','2014-09-11 15:25:52','2014-09-11 22:25:52','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1405',0,'post','',0),(1407,1,'2014-09-15 20:39:46','2014-09-16 03:39:46','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5563/15067304719_66cc0bb5d8_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>A little alcove on the side of the Sangrada Familia in Barcelona, Spain.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oXrSKR</div></div>','Sangrada Familia Alcove','','publish','closed','open','','sangrada-familia-alcove','','','2014-09-15 20:39:46','2014-09-16 03:39:46','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1407',0,'post','',0),(1409,1,'2014-09-22 16:52:53','2014-09-22 23:52:53','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5567/15303075866_b289f4a7c7_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Melanie staring off into the sunset in Kapalua, Maui, HI.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/pjhgiC</div></div>','Woman versus Sea','','publish','closed','open','','woman-versus-sea','','','2014-09-22 16:52:53','2014-09-22 23:52:53','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1409',0,'post','',0),(1411,1,'2014-09-25 16:34:01','2014-09-25 23:34:01','<div><img src=\'https://farm3.staticflickr.com/2950/15168275219_438c07c5cd_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>From the Sangrada Familia, in Barcelona, Spain.\n<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/p7nnLx</div></div>','I see the light','','publish','closed','open','','i-see-the-light','','','2014-09-25 16:34:01','2014-09-25 23:34:01','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1411',0,'post','',0),(1413,1,'2014-10-19 13:55:37','2014-10-19 20:55:37','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5602/14956236163_dd1ba54eba.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div><br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/oMCBWK</div></div>','Tunnel View','','publish','closed','open','','tunnel-view','','','2014-10-19 13:55:37','2014-10-19 20:55:37','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1413',0,'post','',0),(1415,1,'2014-10-21 15:04:53','2014-10-21 22:04:53','<div><img src=\'https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3943/15595428275_ec82b867bd_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>I have this written in the dust on the back of my wife\'s car, thanks Larry Nienkark.  I think this photo is part of the reason why :).\n\nShot last weekend with Larry Nienkark and Bob Bowman at Mono Lake.  Was great spending the weekend in the Eastern Sierras with a group of photographers including Sam Breach,  frederic schmidt, Christopher Bradley, Todd Draper , Lisa Co, Tim Gupta , Cynthia Pyun, Mitchell Weinstock &amp; Swee Oh.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/pL7Dup</div></div>','Fuji Sucks (Not!)','','publish','closed','open','','fuji-sucks-not','','','2014-10-21 15:04:53','2014-10-21 22:04:53','',0,'http://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1415',0,'post','',0),(1417,1,'2014-10-22 20:08:30','2014-10-23 03:08:30','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5606/15581539066_84e42ba8fe_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>The sunset was so gorgeous on my drive home that I had to stop on Treasure Island and capture it.  One of the best