t Australia again.  Excited to get more pictures of Sydney and Melbourne, two fantastic cities.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/si3m2G</div></div>','Going Back Down Under','','publish','closed','open','','going-back-down-under','','','2015-04-24 17:40:08','2015-04-25 00:40:08','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1433',0,'post','',0),(1435,1,'2015-04-28 14:26:18','2015-04-28 21:26:18','<div><img src=\'https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8686/16684380883_04d7976aac.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div><br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/rqkPan</div></div>','1 Liberty Place in Philly #priime','','publish','closed','open','','1-liberty-place-in-philly-priime','','','2015-04-28 14:26:18','2015-04-28 21:26:18','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1435',0,'post','',0),(1438,1,'2015-05-05 21:26:40','2015-05-06 04:26:40','<div><img src=\'https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8824/17179335337_84101fb913_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>What no cars?  Long exposure of the bridge at sunset.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/sb5zSR</div></div>','Lonely Road','','publish','closed','open','','lonely-road','','','2015-05-05 21:26:40','2015-05-06 04:26:40','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1438',0,'post','',0),(1440,1,'2015-05-18 20:42:54','2015-05-19 03:42:54','<div><img src=\'https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7723/17844645815_74fa26e597_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Long exposure of Melbourne, Victoria, Australia from the very nice Capital City Trail along the Yarra River.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tbStva</div></div>','Melbourne in the Fall','','publish','closed','open','','melbourne-in-the-fall','','','2015-05-18 20:42:54','2015-05-19 03:42:54','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1440',0,'post','',0),(1442,1,'2015-05-19 19:49:38','2015-05-20 02:49:38','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5469/17881107925_706096ec10_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Heading back for vacation in July, can\'t wait!  This is from Maui, but this year we\'re heading to Kaui.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tf6mqe</div></div>','More Hawaii Sunsets','','publish','closed','open','','more-hawaii-sunsets','','','2015-05-19 19:49:38','2015-05-20 02:49:38','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1442',0,'post','',0),(1444,1,'2015-05-21 20:19:17','2015-05-22 03:19:17','<div><img src=\'https://farm9.staticflickr.com/8860/17950748192_b88bd62e0d_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Fun with Photoshop tonight.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tmfh3u</div></div>','Mono Lake Manipulation','','publish','closed','open','','mono-lake-manipulation','','','2015-05-21 20:19:17','2015-05-22 03:19:17','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1444',0,'post','',0),(1446,1,'2015-05-22 18:13:11','2015-05-23 01:13:11','<div><img src=\'https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5470/17985878335_02a0dfbc3b_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>My friend Larry walking back to his car in the fog at Mt Tam.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tpmk1B</div></div>','Lone Walker','','publish','closed','open','','lone-walker','','','2015-05-22 18:13:11','2015-05-23 01:13:11','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1446',0,'post','',0),(1448,1,'2015-05-26 21:06:11','2015-05-27 04:06:11','<div><img src=\'https://farm8.staticflickr.com/7796/18147284201_a307fc6dbc_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>From Rocky Point right off the Highway 1.  There\'s a restaurant with a great view here and this is from near the parking lot.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tDBzmn</div></div>','Love to eat here','','publish','closed','open','','love-to-eat-here','','','2015-05-26 21:06:11','2015-05-27 04:06:11','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1448',0,'post','',0),(1450,1,'2015-06-04 21:14:20','2015-06-05 04:14:20','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/458/18290520789_907563250d_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>One thing remarkable about this beach is its sheer length.  I\'m not used to beaches you can look up and down for seemingly miles.  With my good friend Genti, taking a well deserved evening respite from work.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/tSgGAH</div></div>','Newport Beach','','publish','closed','open','','newport-beach','','','2015-06-04 21:14:20','2015-06-05 04:14:20','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1450',0,'post','',0),(1452,1,'2015-07-01 12:37:57','2015-07-01 19:37:57','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/407/19332380575_a0f16b195b_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>I\'m going back to the Oakland Zoo tomorrow with friends and I\'ll probably get a few more snaps for my B&amp;W Tiger series.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vskvdt</div></div>','Regal','','publish','closed','open','','regal','','','2015-07-01 12:37:57','2015-07-01 19:37:57','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1452',0,'post','',0),(1454,1,'2015-07-02 17:51:15','2015-07-03 00:51:15','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/539/19179185508_c7b9f151b3_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Summer fog is a different beast.  It rarely allows you to stay and catch a sunset, at least on the west side of the bay.  It\'s also a fickle beast, as Larry and I watched the fog rolling in from Mt. Tam, we considered heading down to Rodeo Beach, thinking it might be a rare clear summer evening, but as we were thinking about it the fog suddenly shifted from receding to taking over most of Marin County.  Got a lucky moon rise at sunset this evening, and I also got to meet a whole new set of IGers, which was a treat.  What a great day to go out and shoot!<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vdNkEd</div></div>','Creeping Karl','','publish','closed','open','','creeping-karl','','','2015-07-02 17:51:15','2015-07-03 00:51:15','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1454',0,'post','',0),(1456,1,'2015-07-05 20:19:10','2015-07-06 03:19:10','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/341/19454604045_65b4dea87e_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>I\'m heading back to Hawaii in a couple of weeks, so I really need to clear out my backlog of Hawaii photos from last year.  We\'re not going to Maui again this year, which is a shame because this is a beautiful bamboo forest.  I\'m sure Kauai will hold destinations just as magical.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vD8VZF</div></div>','Bamboo Forest','','publish','closed','open','','bamboo-forest','','','2015-07-05 20:19:10','2015-07-06 03:19:10','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1456',0,'post','',0),(1458,1,'2015-07-06 20:01:08','2015-07-07 03:01:08','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/285/19295996768_9b25eb1d69_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>More clearing out of my Hawaii collection. I\'m so looking forward to the sunsets next week.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vp82zs</div></div>','Oh the Sunsets','','publish','closed','open','','oh-the-sunsets','','','2015-07-06 20:01:08','2015-07-07 03:01:08','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1458',0,'post','',0),(1460,1,'2015-07-13 20:13:17','2015-07-14 03:13:17','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/553/19488398530_0ac4823f86_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Beautiful evening at Rodeo Beach a few months ago.  Mostly overcast, the sun just barely broke through the clouds.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vG88Vd</div></div>','Breaking Through','','publish','closed','open','','breaking-through','','','2015-07-13 20:13:17','2015-07-14 03:13:17','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1460',0,'post','',0),(1462,1,'2015-07-16 19:49:37','2015-07-17 02:49:37','<div><img src=\'https://farm1.staticflickr.com/392/19140761073_d9861760f2_b.jpg\' style=\'max-width:600px;\' /><br /><div>Quick shot from my back porch in Kauai.<br /><br />\nvia Flickr http://flic.kr/p/vapppX</div></div>','Back Porch','','publish','closed','open','','back-porch','','','2015-07-16 19:49:37','2015-07-17 02:49:37','',0,'https://clintsharp.wordpress.com/?p=1462',0,'post','',0);
